These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, orchid, amaryllis
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, manager, teacher
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the teacher is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the manager is between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the manager and the person who growsamaryllis##2
11. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the teacher is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the cat and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Flower          | amaryllis     | orchid         | poppy     | sunflower    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | manager   | teacher     |
| Pet   | cat    | horse         | goldfish | lizard         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

