.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, tiparillo, pall-mall
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, poppy, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
| Hobby         | chess     | skydiving   | writing    | filmmaking  |
