 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the swisher-smoker and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in november##2
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person driving the subway##1
12. the person eating lime is the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person eating cauliflower and the dannemann-smoker##2

