 9. the person who likes chestnut is between the scientist and the person traveling to london##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
13. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
14. the person traveling to rome is the american##1

