 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the egyptian is between the person traveling to berlin and the fan of punk##2
 4. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
