 6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the indian is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the spanish is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is the egyptian##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the person playing domino##1
11. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the spanish is on the left of the person playing poker##1
13. the indian is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

